\c 100
\p
\v 1 A Psalm for giving thanks.
\q1 Shout to the Lord, all the earth.
\q1
\v 2 Serve the Lord with gladness,
\q1 Come before him with a joyful noise,
\q1
\v 3 Know that the Lord, he is God,
\q1 He is our maker and we are his,
\q1 We are his people and the sheep of his pasture.
\q1
\v 4 Enter his gates with thanksgiving, his courts with praise,
\q1 Give thanks to him and bless his name.
\q1
\v 5 For the Lord is good,
\q1 His steadfast love is for ever,
\q1 His faithfulness for all generations.